'''伊恩·戈尔丁'''（{{lang-en|Ian Andrew Goldin}}）是一位南非经济学家，[[牛津大学|牛津大学]]教授。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/education/2005/jun/01/highereducation.science|title=Oxford institute to seek solutions to world's problems|last=Ford|first=Liz|date=2005-06-01|newspaper=The Guardian|language=en-GB|issn=0261-3077|access-date=2016-04-21|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327091928/https://www.theguardian.com/education/2005/jun/01/highereducation.science|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/education/2006/oct/24/highereducationprofile.highereducation|title=Ian Goldin: Think global|last=Crace|first=John|date=2006-10-23|newspaper=The Guardian|language=en-GB|issn=0261-3077|access-date=2016-04-21|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327091855/https://www.theguardian.com/education/2006/oct/24/highereducationprofile.highereducation|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.timeshighereducation.com/news/on-the-move/205958.article|title=On the move...|website=Times Higher Education (THE)|access-date=2016-04-21|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327091149/https://www.timeshighereducation.com/news/on-the-move/205958.article|dead-url=no}}</ref>专攻方向为[[全球化|全球化]]和[[发展|发展]]理论。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.balliol.ox.ac.uk/professor-ian-goldin|title=Professor Ian Goldin {{!}} Balliol College, University of Oxford|website=www.balliol.ox.ac.uk|access-date=2016-04-21|archive-date=2020-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201013122117/https://www.balliol.ox.ac.uk/professor-ian-goldin|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.oxfordmartin.ox.ac.uk/director/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120311122439/http://www.oxfordmartin.ox.ac.uk/director/ |archive-date=2012-03-11 |title=Director, Oxford Martin School |publisher=Oxford Martin School |location=UK |accessdate=21 September 2012 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==生平==
出生于[[南非|南非]]，<ref name="Bonorchis ">{{Cite web | title = Inspiring Research At the Dreaming Spires to Benefit the Poor | last = Bonorchis | first = Renée | work =  Business Day | date = 20 September 2006 | accessdate = 2016-03-22 | url = http://allafrica.com/stories/200609200330.html | quote =  }}</ref>先后毕业于[[开普敦大学|开普敦大学]]、[[伦敦政治经济学院|伦敦政治经济学院]]、[[牛津大学|牛津大学]]和[[欧洲工商管理学院|欧洲工商管理学院]]。1996年前担任[[欧洲复兴开发银行|欧洲复兴开发银行]]首席经济学家，[[经济合作与发展组织|经济合作与发展组织]]项目主任，1996年至2001年担任[[南非开发银行|南非开发银行]]首席执行官和[[南非总统|南非总统]][[纳尔逊·曼德拉|纳尔逊·曼德拉]]经济顾问。2001年至2003年担任[[世界银行|世界银行]]发展政策主任，2003年至2006年升任[[世界银行|世界银行]]副行长。2006年创建[[牛津大学马丁学院|牛津大学马丁学院]]并担任创始主任和技术与经济变革项目主任。

